This oil has a beautiful, fresh, green herb taste. Basil and olive oil are two important ingredients in Mediterranean cooking and it was obvious to us that the two fused would be wonderful! This delicious oil has the sweet flavor of fresh basil with a mild buttery olive oil in the background. Tip: Drizzling onto your favorite pasta dishes will add a wonderful flavor component and enhance the taste of your sauces. To make a quick and easy Italian dressing, pair it with Oregano White Balsamic. This is also a fine combination when poured over fresh ripe tomatoes.
